╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                          IJAI CLI - Terminal AI                      ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║ Description:                                                         ║
║   Simple command-line interface for interacting with IJAI models.    ║
║   Streams responses in real-time and supports text-to-speech output. ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║ Installation:                                                        ║
║   1. Ensure Python 3 is installed                                    ║
║   2. Run the installer: ./installer.sh                               ║
║   3. Launch the CLI: ijai_cli                                        ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║ Usage:                                                               ║
║   • Type your question and press Enter                               ║
║   • AI will respond immediately and read out the first sentence      ║
║   • CPU/RAM stats are shown in the corner                            ║
║   • Type 'exit' or 'quit' to leave                                   ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║ Notes:                                                               ║
║   • Model selection is persistent                                    ║
║   • Works on Linux (and WSL for Windows)                             ║
║   • No extra configuration required once installed                   ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

